  "body": "<p><img src=\"https://cf.way2muchnoise.eu/versions/1172382.svg\" alt=\"title\" width=\"169\" height=\"25\" /></p>\n<div><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Forge-blue?style=plastic&amp;link=https%3A%2F%2Ffiles.minecraftforge.net%2Fnet%2Fminecraftforge%2Fforge%2F\" alt=\"Static Badge\" /> <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/NeoForge-lime?style=plastic&amp;link=https%3A%2F%2Fneoforged.net%2F\" alt=\"Static Badge\" /> <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Fabric-yellow?style=plastic&amp;link=https%3A%2F%2Ffabricmc.net%2F\" alt=\"Static Badge\" /></div>\n<p>&nbsp;<br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">This mod allow to use any&nbsp;<a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/numismatics\">Create : Numismatic</a> coins on&nbsp;<a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/bountiful\">Bountiful</a>&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/DevDyna/ContentArchive/blob/main/Create%20Numismatic%20Bounties/screen/base.png?raw=true\" alt=\"image\" width=\"784\" height=\"366\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Also this project still fully compatible with <a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/extra-bounties\">Extra Bounties</a></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/DevDyna/ContentArchive/blob/main/Create%20Numismatic%20Bounties/screen/extra.png?raw=true\" width=\"784\" height=\"366\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
